title: Gunslinger
name: Gunslinger

title: Invasion of the Body Snatchers
name: Invasion of the Body Snatchers

title: Court Jester, The
name: The Court Jester

title: Witness for the Prosecution

title: Rosemary's Baby
name: Rosemary's Baby
description: A young couple trying for a baby moves into an aging, ornate apartment building on Central Park West, where they find themselves surrounded by peculiar neighbors.

title: 2001: A Space Odyssey
name: 2001: A Space Odyssey
description: After uncovering a mysterious artifact buried beneath the Lunar surface, a spacecraft is sent to Jupiter to find its origins - a spacecraft manned by two men and the supercomputer H.A.L. 9000.

title: Where Eagles Dare
name: Where Eagles Dare
description: Allied agents stage a daring raid on a castle where the Nazis are holding American brigadier general George Carnaby prisoner, but that's not all that's really going on.

title: Yellow Submarine
name: Yellow Submarine
description: The Beatles agree to accompany Captain Fred in his yellow submarine and go to Pepperland to free it from the music-hating Blue Meanies.

title: Star!
name: 星星星
description: A musical biography of Gertrude Lawrence, who led a hustling and bustling life on the stage.

title: Hellfighters
name: Hellfighters
description: Divorced Chance Buckman fights international oil rig fires. An injury brings his daughter and to his dismay, she weds Greg, a team member. Chance gets a desk-job, so he and Madelyn remarry, but a Venezuelan oil rig fire reunites them.

title: Barbarella
name: Barbarella
stars_name: Jane Fonda,John Phillip Law,Anita Pallenberg,Milo O'Shea
description: Barbarella, an astronaut from the 41st century, sets out to find and stop the evil scientist Durand Durand, whose Positronic Ray threatens to bring evil back into the galaxy.

title: Once Upon a Time in the West
name: Once Upon a Time in the West
description: A mysterious stranger with a harmonica joins forces with a notorious desperado to protect a beautiful widow from a ruthless assassin working for the railroad.

title: Lion in Winter, The
name: 冬之獅
description: 1183 A.D.: King Henry II's three sons all want to inherit the throne, but he won't commit to a choice. When he allows his imprisoned wife Eleanor of Aquitaine out for a Christmas visit, they all variously plot to force him into a decision.

title: If....
name: If....
description: In this allegorical story, a revolution led by pupil Mick Travis takes place at an old established private school in England.

title: Head
name: Head
description: The Monkees are tossed about in a psychedelic, surrealist, plotless, circular bit of fun fluff.

title: Hang 'Em High
name: Hang 'Em High
description: When an innocent man barely survives a lynching, he returns as a lawman determined to bring the vigilantes to justice.

title: Night of the Living Dead
name: Night of the Living Dead
description: A ragtag group of Pennsylvanians barricade themselves in an old farmhouse to remain safe from a horde of flesh-eating ghouls that are ravaging the East Coast of the United States.

title: Carry On... Up the Khyber
name: Carry on Up the Khyber
description: Sir Sidney Ruff-Diamond looks after the British outpost near the Khyber Pass. Protected by the kilted Third Foot and Mouth regiment, you would think they were safe but the Khazi of Kalabar has other ideas.

title: Bride Wore Black, The
name: The Bride Wore Black
description: Julie Kohler is prevented from suicide by her mother. She leaves the town. She will track down, charm and kill five men who do not know her. What is her goal? What is her purpose?

title: Asterix et Cleopatre
name: Astérix et Cléopâtre
description: Ordered by Cleopatra to build a palace in Alexandria within three months as part of a bet with Caesar, an architect enlists the help of Asterix, Obelix and Getafix.

title: Funny Girl
name: 妙女郎
description: The life of Fanny Brice, famed comedienne and entertainer of the early 1900s. We see her rise to fame as a Ziegfeld girl, subsequent career, and her personal life, particularly her relationship with Nick Arnstein.

title: Hour of the Wolf
name: Hour of the Wolf
stars_name: Max von Sydow,Liv Ullmann,Gertrud Fridh,Georg Rydeberg
description: While vacationing on a remote German island with his younger pregnant wife, an artist has an emotional breakdown while confronting his repressed desires.

title: Destroy All Monsters
name: Destroy All Monsters
description: At the turn of the century, Earth's monsters have been safely rounded up and studied on Monsterland. Chaos erupts when a race of she-aliens known as the Kilaaks unleashes the monsters across the world.

title: Il giorno della civetta
name: Mafia
stars_name: Claudia Cardinale,Franco Nero,Lee J. Cobb,Tano Cimarosa
description: Following a murder in a small Sicilian town, the new chief of the Carabinieri must fight corrupt officials, the frightened silence of witnesses and the local Mafia boss in order to solve the case.

title: Gamera vs. Viras
name: Gamera vs. Viras
description: Gamera the Flying Turtle falls under the spell of evil aliens, but two children free him and he returns to fight the aliens' monster, Viras.

title: Bullitt
name: Bullitt
description: An all-guts, no-glory San Francisco cop becomes determined to find the underworld kingpin that killed the witness in his protection.

title: Ice Station Zebra
name: Ice Station Zebra
description: USN nuclear sub USS Tigerfish must rush to the North Pole to rescue the staff of Drift Ice Station Zebra weather station.

title: Dracula Has Risen from the Grave
name: Dracula Has Risen from the Grave
description: When Castle Dracula is exorcised by the Monsignor, it accidentally brings the Count back from the dead. Dracula follows the Monsignor back to his hometown, preying on the holy man's beautiful niece and her friends.

title: Egri csillagok
name: Egri csillagok
description: 1552, the great Turkish Empire wants to conquer Europe, and the world. The last stand is Hungarian Kingdom, and the castle of Eger. The brave soldiers decides they will fight till the end of their lifes.

title: Wrecking Crew, The
name: The Wrecking Crew
description: Gold bullion worth USD 1 billion has been stolen from a hijacked train in Denmark. The main suspect is Count Massimo Contini. The US government sends Matt Helm, one of its top agents, to investigate and recover the gold.

title: Chitty Chitty Bang Bang
name: 飛天萬能車
stars_name: Dick Van Dyke,Sally Ann Howes,Lionel Jeffries,Benny Hill
description: A down-on-his-luck inventor turns a broken-down Grand Prix car into a fancy vehicle for his children, and then they go off on a magical fantasy adventure to save their grandfather in a far-off land.

title: Today We Kill, Tomorrow We Die!
name: Today We Kill, Tomorrow We Die!
description: A man released after a jail term for a crime he did not commit, raises a gang to go after the man who framed him.

title: Oliver!
name: 孤雛淚
description: After being sold to a mortician, young orphan Oliver Twist runs away and meets a group of boys trained to be pickpockets by an elderly mentor in 1830s London.

title: Valley of Death, The
name: The Valley of Death
description: An army gold shipment and its escort vanish in the Ozarks, prompting accusations of theft and desertion but frontiersman Old Shatterhand and Apache chief Winnetou help solve the mystery of the missing army gold.

title: Django, Prepare a Coffin
name: Django, Prepare a Coffin
description: A gunfighter forms a gang of "deceased" execution victims to get revenge on the politician and outlaw who killed his wife.

title: Rape of the Vampire, The
name: The Rape of the Vampire
description: After a psychoanalyst unsuccessfully tries to convince four sisters that they are not 200 year old vampires, the Queen of the Vampires promulgates the cause of the Undead.

title: Honeymoon Killers, The
name: The Honeymoon Killers
stars_name: Shirley Stoler,Tony Lo Bianco,Mary Jane Higby,Doris Roberts
description: An obese, embittered nurse doesn't mind if her toupee-wearing boyfriend romances and fleeces other women, as long as he takes her along on his con jobs.

title: Support Your Local Sheriff!
name: Support Your Local Sheriff!
description: In the old west, a man becomes a Sheriff just for the pay, figuring he can decamp if things get tough. In the end, he uses ingenuity instead.

title: My Side of the Mountain
name: My Side of the Mountain
description: As young Sam Gribley runs away he learns about nature.

title: Paint Your Wagon
name: 長征萬寶山
description: Two unlikely prospector partners share the same wife in a California gold rush mining town.

title: Butch Cassidy and the Sundance Kid
name: Butch Cassidy and the Sundance Kid
description: Wyoming, early 1900s. Butch Cassidy and The Sundance Kid are the leaders of a band of outlaws. After a train robbery goes wrong they find themselves on the run with a posse hard on their heels. Their solution - escape to Bolivia.

title: Easy Rider
name: Easy Rider
description: Two bikers head from L.A. to New Orleans through the open country and desert lands, and along the way they meet a man who bridges a counter-culture gap of which they had been unaware.

title: Computer Wore Tennis Shoes, The
name: The Computer Wore Tennis Shoes
description: At Medfield College, an accident with a donated computer gives Dexter Riley the ability to remember any knowledge learned instantly and perfectly.

title: Downhill Racer
name: Downhill Racer
stars_name: Robert Redford,Gene Hackman,Camilla Sparv,Karl Michael Vogler
description: Quietly cocky Robert Redford joins U.S. ski team as downhill racer and clashes with the team's coach, played by Gene Hackman. Lots of good skiing action leading to an exciting climax.

title: Italian Job, The
name: The Italian Job
description: Comic caper movie about a plan to steal a gold shipment from the streets of Turin by creating a traffic jam.

title: True Grit
name: True Grit
description: A drunken, hard-nosed U.S. Marshal and a Texas Ranger help a stubborn teenager track down her father's murderer in Indian Territory.

title: Alice's Restaurant
name: Alice's Restaurant
description: A cinematic adaption of Arlo Guthrie's classic song story.

title: Mississippi Mermaid
name: Mississippi Mermaid
description: A wealthy plantation owner is captivated by a mysterious woman with a shady past.

title: Army of Shadows
name: Army of Shadows
description: An account of underground resistance fighters in Nazi-occupied France.

title: On Her Majesty's Secret Service
name: On Her Majesty's Secret Service
description: James Bond woos a mob boss' daughter and goes undercover to uncover the true reason for Ernst Stavro Blofeld's allergy research in the Swiss Alps involving beautiful women from around the world.

title: Hello, Dolly!
name: 我愛紅娘
description: Matchmaker Dolly Levi travels to Yonkers to find a partner for "half-a-millionaire" Horace Vandergelder, convincing his niece, his niece's intended, and his two clerks to travel to New York City along the way.

title: Godzilla's Revenge (Godzilla, Minira, Gabara: All Monsters Attack)
name: All Monsters Attack
description: A latchkey child living in the industrial city of Kawasaki confronts his loneliness through his escapist dreams of Monster Island and friendship with Minilla.

title: Age of Consent
name: Age of Consent
description: A grizzled Australian painter decides to jolt his stale creativity by moving to a remote island on the Great Barrier Reef, where he takes on an alluring, uninhibited young woman as his muse.

title: Take the Money and Run
name: Take the Money and Run
description: The life and times of Virgil Starkwell, inept bank robber.

title: Z
name: Z
description: The public murder of a prominent politician and doctor amid a violent demonstration is covered up by military and government officials. A tenacious magistrate is determined not to let them get away with it.

title: Swimming Pool, The
name: La Piscine
description: Lovers Marianne and Jean-Paul spend their vacation in a villa on the French Riviera near St-Tropez. Marianne invites her former lover, Harry, and his teenage daughter to stay. Tension rises between them, especially when Jean-Paul seduces Penelope.

title: Django the Bastard
name: Django the Bastard
description: A mysterious stranger appears to take terrifying revenge on former Confederate officers who during the Civil War betrayed and were responsible for the massacre of their unit.

title: Le Cercle Rouge
name: Le Cercle Rouge
description: After leaving prison, master thief Corey crosses paths with a notorious escapee and an alcoholic former policeman. The trio proceed to plot an elaborate heist.

title: Beyond the Valley of the Dolls
name: Beyond the Valley of the Dolls
description: Three girls come to Hollywood to make it big, but find only sex, drugs and sleaze.

title: AristoCats, The
name: 貓兒歷險記
description: With the help of a smooth talking tomcat, a family of Parisian felines set to inherit a fortune from their owner try to make it back home after a jealous butler kidnaps them and leaves them in the country.

title: Santa Clause is Comin' to Town
name: Santa Claus Is Comin' to Town
description: A mailman reveals the origin of Santa Claus.

title: Phantom Tollbooth, The
name: The Phantom Tollbooth
description: Milo is a boy who is bored with life. One day he comes home to find a toll booth in his room. Having nothing better to do, he gets in his toy car and drives through - only to emerge in a world full of adventure.

title: Two Mules for Sister Sara
name: Two Mules for Sister Sara
description: Nun Sara (Shirley MacLaine) is on the run in Mexico and is saved from cowboys by Hogan (Clint Eastwood), who is preparing for a future mission to capture a French fort. The pair become good friends, but Sara never does tell him the true reason behind her being outlawed.

title: Vampire Lovers, The
name: The Vampire Lovers
description: Seductive vampire Carmilla Karnstein and her family target the beautiful and the rich in a remote area of late eighteenth-century Gemany.

title: Scars of Dracula
name: Scars of Dracula
description: A young man, Paul Carlson, is on a trip and spends the night at Count Dracula's castle. He is murdered. After some time has passed, the young man's brother Simon comes to the small town where all the traces end to look for him.

title: Taste the Blood of Dracula
name: Taste the Blood of Dracula
description: Three distinguished English gentlemen accidentally resurrect Count Dracula, killing a disciple of his in process. The Count seeks to avenge his dead servant, by making the trio die in the hands of their own children.

title: House of Dark Shadows
name: House of Dark Shadows
stars_name: Jonathan Frid,Grayson Hall,Kathryn Leigh Scott,Roger Davis
description: Vampire Barnabas Collins is accidentally released from his centuries-long confinement at his family's estate in Maine. He targets his clueless descendants who live there now and pursues Maggie, the incarnation of his lost love.

title: Airport
name: Airport
description: A bomber on board an airplane, an airport almost closed by snow, and various personal problems of the people involved.

title: Music Lovers, The
name: The Music Lovers
description: Piano teacher Peter Ilych Tchaikovsky struggles against his homosexuality by marrying, but unfortunately he chooses a nymphomaniac whom he cannot satisfy.

title: Darling Lili
name: 拂曉出擊
description: Set during World War I, this movie is a cute spin on the Mata Hari legend.

title: Colossus: The Forbin Project
name: Colossus: The Forbin Project
description: Thinking this will prevent war, the US government gives an impenetrable supercomputer total control over launching nuclear missiles. But what the computer does with the power is unimaginable to its creators.

title: Nachts, wenn Dracula erwacht
name: Count Dracula
description: Count Dracula, a gray-haired vampire who regains his youth by dining on the blood of maidens, is pursued in London and Transylvania by Professor Van Helsing, Jonathan Harker and Quincey Morris after he victimizes them and their loved ones.

title: Donkey Skin
name: Peau d'âne
description: A fairy godmother helps a princess disguise and flee the kingdom so she won't have to marry the king who happens to be her father.

title: Little Big Man
name: Little Big Man
stars_name: Dustin Hoffman,Faye Dunaway,Chief Dan George,Martin Balsam
description: Jack Crabb, looking back from extreme old age, tells of his life being raised by Native Americans and fighting with General Custer.

title: Waterloo
name: 滑鐵盧戰役
description: Facing the decline of everything he has worked to obtain, conqueror Napoleon Bonaparte and his army confront the British at the Battle of Waterloo.

title: Tora! Tora! Tora!
name: 偷襲珍珠港
description: The story of the 1941 Japanese air raid on Pearl Harbor, and the series of preceding American blunders that aggravated its effectiveness.

title: Catch-22
name: Catch-22
description: A man is trying desperately to be certified insane during World War II, so he can stop flying missions.

title: Wanda
name: Wanda
description: Wanda, a lonely housewife, drifts through mining country until she meets a petty thief who takes her in.

title: They Call Me Trinity
name: They Call Me Trinity
description: A lazy, unorthodox gunfighter and his portly, horse-thieving brother defend a Mormon settlement from a land-grabbing Major, a Mexican bandit, and their henchmen.

title: Pippi in the South Seas
name: Pippi in the South Seas
description: With the help of her friends Tommy and Annika, Pippi Longstocking ventures to the South Pacific island Porto Piluse to rescue her father, who was captured by ruthless pirates.

title: Rio Lobo
name: Rio Lobo
description: After the Civil War, Cord McNally searches for the two traitors whose treachery caused the defeat of McNally's unit and the loss of a close friend.

title: Patton
name: Patton
stars_name: George C. Scott,Karl Malden,Stephen Young,Michael Strong
description: The World War II phase of the career of controversial American general George S. Patton.

title: Le Boucher
name: Le Boucher
description: An unlikely friendship between a dour, working class butcher and a repressed schoolteacher coincides with a grisly series of Ripper-type murders in a provincial French town.

title: Walkabout
name: Walkabout
description: Two city-bred siblings are stranded in the Australian Outback, where they learn to survive with the aid of an Aboriginal boy on his "walkabout": a ritual separation from his tribe.

title: Willy Wonka & the Chocolate Factory
name: 歡樂糖果屋
description: A poor but hopeful boy seeks one of the five coveted golden tickets that will send him on a tour of Willy Wonka's mysterious chocolate factory.

title: THX 1138
name: THX 1138
stars_name: Robert Duvall,Donald Pleasence,Don Pedro Colley,Maggie McOmie
description: In the 25th century, a time when people have designations instead of names, a man, THX 1138, and a woman, LUH 3417, rebel against their rigidly-controlled society.

title: A Clockwork Orange
name: A Clockwork Orange
description: In the future, a sadistic gang leader is imprisoned and volunteers for a conduct-aversion experiment, but it doesn't go as planned.

title: Million Dollar Duck, The
name: The Million Dollar Duck
description: Professor Dooley takes home a duck from his research laboratory as a pet for his son, but soon finds out that it lays golden eggs.

title: Taking Off
name: Taking Off
description: While searching for their runaway teenage daughter, the parents rediscover life's joys as they get acquainted with a self-help group for parents of vanished children.

title: Here Comes Peter Cotton Tail
name: Here Comes Peter Cottontail
description: With the help of a time machine, Peter Cottontail must rescue Easter from the hands of the malicious Irontail.

title: Bedknobs and Broomsticks
name: 飛天萬能床
description: An apprentice witch, three kids and a cynical magician conman search for the missing component to a magic spell to be used in the defense of Britain in World War II.

title: Straw Dogs
name: Straw Dogs
description: A young American and his English wife come to rural England and face increasingly vicious local harassment.

title: Shaft
name: Shaft
stars_name: Richard Roundtree,Moses Gunn,Charles Cioffi,Christopher St. John
description: Cool black private eye John Shaft is hired by a crime lord to find and retrieve his kidnapped daughter.

title: Escape from the Planet of the Apes
name: Escape from the Planet of the Apes
description: The world is shocked by the appearance of three talking chimpanzees, who arrived mysteriously in a U.S. spacecraft. They become the toast of society, but one man believes them to be a threat to the human race.

title: Sweet Sweetback's Baadasssss Song
name: Sweet Sweetback's Baadasssss Song
stars_name: Melvin Van Peebles,Hubert Scales,John Dullaghan,Simon Chuckster
description: After saving a Black Panther from some racist cops, a black male prostitute goes on the run from "the man" with the help of the ghetto community and some disillusioned Hells Angels.

title: Mrs. Pollifax - Spy
name: Mrs. Pollifax-Spy
description: A widowed New Jerseyan woman volunteers for spy duty at the CIA, being in her own opinion, expendable now that the children are grown, and is assigned to pick up a book in Mexico City, while finding out that it is easier said than done.

title: Play Misty for Me
name: Play Misty for Me
description: The life of a disc jockey is turned upside down after a romantic encounter with an obsessed fan.

title: Frenchie King
name: The Legend of Frenchie King
stars_name: Brigitte Bardot,Claudia Cardinale,Michael J. Pollard,Micheline Presle
description: Outlaw sisters in the old West inherit a ranch and try to settle down and develop relationships with neighboring family of lots of brothers.

title: Mary, Queen of Scots
name: Mary, Queen of Scots
description: During the sixteenth century, the Catholic Mary, Queen of Scots engages in over two decades of religious and political conflict with her cousin, the Protestant Queen Elizabeth I of England, amidst political intrigue in her native land.

title: Lust for a Vampire
name: Lust for a Vampire
description: In 1830, forty years to the day since the last manifestation of their dreaded vampirism, the Karnstein heirs use the blood of an innocent to bring forth the evil that is the beautiful Mircalla - or as she was in 1710, Carmilla.

title: Let's Scare Jessica to Death
name: Let's Scare Jessica to Death
description: A recently institutionalized woman has bizarre experiences after moving into a supposedly haunted country farmhouse and fears she may be losing her sanity once again.

title: French Connection, The
name: The French Connection
stars_name: Gene Hackman,Roy Scheider,Fernando Rey,Tony Lo Bianco
description: A pair of NYPD detectives in the Narcotics Bureau stumble onto a heroin smuggling ring based in Marseilles, but stopping them and capturing their leaders proves an elusive goal.

title: McCabe & Mrs. Miller
name: McCabe & Mrs. Miller
description: A gambler and a prostitute become business partners in a remote Old West mining town, and their enterprise thrives until a large corporation arrives on the scene.

title: Lady Hermit, The
name: The Lady Hermit
description: Martial arts star Cheng Pei pei and versatile director Ho Meng hua were a great team, who elevated this tale of a virtuous swordswoman's revenge on the Black Demon who injured her to one of the best of both their careers.

title: Diamonds Are Forever
name: Diamonds Are Forever
stars_name: Sean Connery,Jill St. John,Charles Gray,Lana Wood
description: A diamond smuggling investigation leads James Bond to Las Vegas, where he uncovers an evil plot involving a rich business tycoon.

title: Duel
name: Duel
description: A business commuter is pursued and terrorized by the malevolent driver of a massive tractor-trailer.

title: Godzilla vs. the Smog Monster (Godzilla vs. Hedorah)
name: Godzilla vs. Hedorah
description: An ever evolving alien life-form from the Dark Gaseous Nebula arrives to consume rampant pollution. Spewing mists of sulfuric acid and corrosive sludge, neither humanity or Godzilla may be able to defeat this toxic menace.

title: Wake in Fright
name: Wake in Fright
description: After a bad gambling bet, a schoolteacher is marooned in a town full of crazy, drunk, violent men who threaten to make him just as crazy, drunk, and violent.

title: Klute
name: Klute
description: A small-town detective searching for a missing man has only one lead: a connection with a New York prostitute.

title: House That Dripped Blood, The
name: The House That Dripped Blood
description: An anthology of four horror stories revolving around a mysterious rental house in the U.K.

title: Devils, The
name: The Devils
description: In 17th-century France, Father Urbain Grandier seeks to protect the city of Loudun from the corrupt establishment of Cardinal Richelieu. Hysteria occurs within the city when he is accused of witchcraft by a sexually-repressed nun.

title: Nicholas and Alexandra
name: Nicholas and Alexandra
description: Tsar Nicholas II, the inept last monarch of Russia, insensitive to the needs of his people, is overthrown and exiled to Siberia with his family.

title: Vampyros Lesbos
name: Vampyros Lesbos
description: An erotic horror tale about a vixen vampiress seducing and killing women to appease her insatiable thirst for female blood.

title: Get Carter
name: Get Carter
description: When his brother dies under mysterious circumstances in a car accident, London gangster Jack Carter travels to Newcastle to investigate.

title: 10 Rillington Place
name: 10 Rillington Place
description: What happened to the women at 10 Rillington Place? The story of British serial killer John Christie, who committed most or all of his crimes in the titular terraced house, and the miscarriage of justice involving Timothy Evans.

title: Macbeth
name: 森林復活記
description: A ruthlessly ambitious Scottish lord seizes the throne with the help of his scheming wife and a trio of witches.

title: Werewolves on Wheels
name: Werewolves on Wheels
description: A biker gang and its leader fall prey to a satan worshipper and his cult.

title: Hannie Caulder
name: Hannie Caulder
description: After she is raped and her husband murdered, a woman hires a bounty hunter to instruct her in the use of a gun so she can get her revenge on the three outlaws responsible.

title: Emigrants, The
name: Utvandrarna
stars_name: Max von Sydow,Liv Ullmann,Eddie Axberg,Sven-Olof Bern
description: Småland, Sweden, mid-19th century. A farming family struggle with their rocky, unyielding land, and decide to embark on the arduous journey to new hope in America.

title: Punishment Park
name: Punishment Park
description: "Punishment Park" is a pseudo-documentary purporting to be a film crews's news coverage of the team of soldiers escorting a group of hippies, draft dodgers, and anti-establishment types ...                See full summary »

title: Daughters of Darkness
name: Daughters of Darkness
description: While passing through a vacation resort, a newlywed couple encounters a mysterious, strikingly beautiful countess and her aide.

title: Vanishing Point
name: Vanishing Point
description: During the 1970s, car delivery driver Kowalski delivers hot rods in record time but always runs into trouble with the highway cops.

title: Anand
name: Anand
description: The story of a terminally ill man who wishes to live life to the fullest before the inevitable occurs, as told by his best friend.

title: Trinity Is Still My Name
name: Trinity Is Still My Name
description: Bambino tries to teach his brother Trinity how to become an outlaw, but the two wind up saving a pioneer family and breaking up an arms ring instead.

title: Johnny Got His Gun
name: Johnny Got His Gun
description: During World War I, a patriotic young American is rendered blind, deaf, limbless, and mute by a horrific artillery shell attack. Trapped in what's left of his body, he desperately looks for a way to end his life.

title: Andromeda Strain, The
name: The Andromeda Strain
description: A team of top scientists work feverishly in a secret, state-of-the-art laboratory to discover what has killed the citizens of a small town and learn how this deadly contagion can be stopped.

title: Solyaris
name: Solaris
description: A psychologist is sent to a station orbiting a distant planet in order to discover what has caused the crew to go insane.

title: Pink Flamingos
name: Pink Flamingos
description: Notorious Baltimore criminal and underground figure Divine goes up against a sleazy married couple who make a passionate attempt to humiliate her and seize her tabloid-given title as "The Filthiest Person Alive".

title: Une belle fille comme moi
name: A Gorgeous Girl Like Me
description: Stanislas Previne is a young sociologist, preparing a thesis on criminal women. He meets in prison Camille Bliss to interview her. Camille is accused to have murdered her lover Arthur and ...                See full summary »

title: When Michael Calls
name: When Michael Calls
description: A woman begins to receive ominous phone calls from her nephew, who died 15 years earlier. With each phone call, a family member dies. Will she be the next in line?

title: Godfather, The
name: The Godfather
description: The aging patriarch of an organized crime dynasty in postwar New York City transfers control of his clandestine empire to his reluctant youngest son.

title: Aguirre: The Wrath of God
name: 天譴
description: In the 16th century, the ruthless and insane Don Lope de Aguirre leads a Spanish expedition in search of El Dorado.

title: Don't Torture a Duckling
name: Don't Torture a Duckling
description: When a southern Italian town is rocked by a string of child murders, the police and two urban outcasts search for the culprit amid scapegoating within the superstitious community.

title: Deliverance
name: Deliverance
description: Intent on seeing the Cahulawassee River before it's dammed and turned into a lake, outdoor fanatic Lewis Medlock takes his friends on a canoeing trip they'll never forget into the dangerous American back-country.

title: Jeremiah Johnson
name: Jeremiah Johnson
description: A mountain man who wishes to live the life of a hermit becomes the unwilling object of a long vendetta by the Crow tribe and proves to be a match for their warriors in single combat on the early frontier.

stars_name: William Daniels,Howard Da Silva,Ken Howard,Donald Madden
description: A musical retelling of the American Revolution's political struggle in the Continental Congress to declare independence.

title: Travels With My Aunt
name: Travels with My Aunt
stars_name: Maggie Smith,Alec McCowen,Louis Gossett Jr.,Robert Stephens
description: At his mother's funeral, banker Henry meets his Aunt Augusta, an eccentric old woman who takes him on a wild adventure to rescue an old lover.

title: Butterflies Are Free
name: Butterflies Are Free
stars_name: Goldie Hawn,Edward Albert,Eileen Heckart,Paul Michael Glaser
description: A blind man moves into his own apartment against the wishes of his overprotective mother and befriends the freethinking young woman next door.

title: Dawns Here are Quiet, The
name: A zori zdes tikhie
